msgid "Turn this on if Weather Please's reported UV index is consistently lower than local sources."
msgstr "Aktifkan ini jika indeks UV yang dilaporkan Weather Please secara konsisten lebih rendah daripada sumber lokal."

#: src/pages/index.tsx:185
msgid "Unable to fetch weather data. Please check your internet connection and try again."
msgstr "Tidak dapat mengambil data cuaca. Periksa koneksi internet Anda dan coba lagi."

